// Rust port of Logger.core.cs. Provides a small leveled logging facade that
// writes timestamped lines to stderr and to a per-program, day-rolling log
// file. The verbose .NET LogWriter hierarchy is collapsed into one writer; the
// public surface (error/warning/info/debug) matches the original.
